title: #92Noon Nordo in for PA!  Britt/Johnson/Russo/Bailey
description: Live from TCO Performance Center, Nordo is in for PA and joined by guests from all around the sports world for a fun show.  Britt   joins the show to discuss the Timberwolves recent struggles, Ron Johnson is in studio for plenty of Vikings conversation, Michael Russo calls in for some updates on the Wild, and Vikings kicker Dan Bailey
